latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Dear thin pig,

That one person who accepts whatever I say😭💓 nange swalpa kopa jasthi sometimes Bega react madthini but she will not 😘 ( Oly in my case Huh bere avaru try madbedi 200% vappas siguthe 😂😂 ) 💕 people are gonna come and go but I will always have your back😌❤U mean a lot to me😰💓 !!
